your daddy's house.

16:50.694 --> 16:53.094
All right, we got another
shout-out to my man, Rel.

16:53.129 --> 16:55.430
He just blew it
with Frank the barber's girl.

16:55.465 --> 16:57.498
But it's all good, y'all,

16:57.534 --> 17:00.068
