17:06.976 --> 17:10.678
You told a DJ to shout out

17:10.714 --> 17:12.847
that you were with
Frank the barber's girl?

17:12.882 --> 17:14.215
And then asked her

17:14.250 --> 17:16.751
to have some weird
glasses revenge sex,

17:16.786 --> 17:18.619
-or whatever the hell that is.
-B-But...

17:20.056 --> 17:22.623
Okay, I didn't say anything
about her boots,

17:22.659 --> 17:24.859
and believe me,
they was loose as hell.

17:24.894 --> 17:27.962
Rel, listen, everyone
knows about the barber,

17:27.997 --> 17:31.299
and whatever respect you
had left is gone. You know why?

17:31.334 --> 17:33.701
Because you chose to handle this
like a child.

17:33.737 --> 17:35.603
You're right, all right? I...

17:35.638 --> 17:37.772
Yo, if I'm gonna clear my name
in the streets,

17:37.807 --> 17:39.907
