with Frank directly.

17:39.943 --> 17:41.876
That's what I'm talking about,
big bro.

17:41.911 --> 17:43.177
Prison yard rules.

17:44.848 --> 17:47.548
Somebody disrespect you,
walk up to 'em,

17:47.584 --> 17:48.883
