17:48.918 --> 17:51.886
put your hand on their shoulder,
and shank 'em.

17:51.921 --> 17:53.154
What?

17:53.189 --> 17:57.925
Boy, get your ass over here.

17:57.961 --> 18:01.329
You can't just go around
shanking people in regular life.

18:02.332 --> 18:03.731
