18:54.517 --> 18:58.519
Damn. So you know about that.

18:58.555 --> 18:59.987
Man, everybody knows about it.

19:00.023 --> 19:01.455
Hey, bro, that was
my wife, okay?

19:01.491 --> 19:03.291
I lost my family,
and it's all your fault.

19:03.326 --> 19:05.793
