saying it was all my fault?

19:05.829 --> 19:07.795
Yes, it was all of your fault.

19:07.831 --> 19:09.363
So you putting this all on me?

19:09.399 --> 19:12.400
Brother, are you deaf?

19:12.435 --> 19:14.335
Okay, yes.
Who else would I put it on?

19:14.370 --> 19:15.536
You.

19:15.572 --> 19:17.572
Me?

19:17.607 --> 19:21.309
Look, Rel, you trying to tell me
that you was this great husband?

19:21.344 --> 19:23.477
Shannon said that you
never even listened to her.

19:23.513 --> 19:26.147
-You never even asked her
about her dreams...
-Okay, loo-loo-loo-look.

19:26.182 --> 19:28.683
